PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774271470
OL,3,CIran strikes near Israel's main
OL,4,Cnuclear research site
OL,6,FThe Israeli military said its defenses
OL,7,Fwere not able to intercept missiles
OL,8,Fthat hit the southern cities of Dimona
OL,9,Fand Arad.
OL,11,FDozens of people were injured,
OL,12,Femergency services said.
OL,14,FEarlier Iran's Natanz nuclear
OL,15,Fenrichment facility was hit in an
OL,16,Fairstrike, according to an official
OL,17,FIranian news agency, which said there
OL,18,Fwas no radiation leakage.
OL,20,FIsrael denied responsibility, and the
OL,21,FPentagon declined to comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774271470
OL,3,CIran strikes near Israel's main
OL,4,Cnuclear research site
OL,6,FThe UN nuclear watchdog has said the
OL,7,Fbulk of Iran's estimated 970 pounds
OL,8,F(440 kilograms) of enriched uranium is
OL,9,Felsewhere, beneath the rubble at its
OL,10,FIsfahan facility.
OL,12,FThe International Atomic Energy Agency
OL,13,Fsaid on X it was looking into the
OL,14,Fstrike.
OL,16,FNatanz was also hit in the first week
OL,17,Fof the war and in the 12-day war last
OL,18,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
