PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774271470
OL,3,CIran strikes near Israel's main
OL,4,Cnuclear research site
OL,6,FRussian Foreign Ministry spokesperson
OL,7,FMaria Zakharova said such strikes
OL,8,Fposed a "real risk of catastrophic
OL,9,Fdisaster throughout the Middle East."
OL,11,FIsrael is believed to be the only
OL,12,FMiddle East nation with nuclear
OL,13,Fweapons, though its leaders refuse to
OL,14,Fconfirm or deny their existence.
OL,16,FThe IAEA said on X it had not received
OL,17,Freports of damage to the Israeli
OL,18,Fcenter or abnormal radiation levels.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@eO]
