OL,3,CIran strikes near Israel's main
OL,4,Cnuclear research site
OL,6,FEarlier, Iran targeted the joint UK-US
OL,7,FDiego Garcia military base in the
OL,8,FIndian Ocean about 2,500 miles (4,000
OL,9,Fkilometers) away, suggesting that
OL,10,FTehran has missiles that can go
OL,11,Ffarther than previously acknowledged `
OL,12,For that it had used its space program
OL,13,Ffor an improvised launch.
OL,15,FResidents said Iran's capital saw
OL,16,Fheavy airstrikes as they marked the
OL,17,Fend of the holy month of Ramadan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
