PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774271470
OL,3,CIran strikes near Israel's main
OL,4,Cnuclear research site
OL,6,FThe US and Israel have offered
OL,7,Fshifting rationales for the war, from
OL,8,Fhoping to foment an uprising that
OL,9,Ftopples Iran's leadership to
OL,10,Feliminating its nuclear and missile
OL,11,Fprograms and its support for armed
OL,12,Fproxies.
OL,14,FThere have been no signs of an
OL,15,Fuprising, while internet restrictions
OL,16,Flimit information from Iran.
OL,18,FThe war's effects are felt far beyond
OL,19,Fthe Middle East, raising food and fuel
OL,20,Fprices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
